table_foot: Data shown are n (%) or median (first and third quartiles). For continuous variables, p-values are from Mann-Whitney test. For categorical variables, p-values are from Pearson’s Chi-squared test. Key; MoCA, Montreal Cognitive Assessment; CDR, Clinical Dementia Rating Scale; AVLT-RPC, Rey Auditory Verbal Learning Test – Recognition Percent Correct; RBD, Rapid eye movement sleep behavior disorder.
